_sText:
Here it is Hoejkontor, i used alot of my time on it and its my first real map. Its Bomb/Defuse map and its very fun to play. I know there no lightning or envioment lightning simply cause it fucked it all up lol. In the map is some elements from the Hoejhus9, exsample the T-Roof but i did so you cant really camp up there. You'll see. The reason why there is so many elements from the Hoejhus9 is that alot of them are great! I shield of the "bridge" because i hate when people B-hop down to CT-spawn too fast lol. The Big Pole at the top can be "used" by clicking the buttom side turning against T-spawn and a bomb will be spawnd. (And some explosion and stuff will happen) Theres a elevator. A monitor at CT-spawn connected to a camera on top. A hole that can break on top of Bombsite (almost invinsible) I've used alot of diffrent things explosion, sounds, shake etc. I've messed around with alot of things.

RATE THE MAP! ;)
